# Sky-cli bug.list
# Full codebase bug scan ‚Äî status as of 2026-07-21 (main).
# Ask the agent: "read bug.list" or "summarize open bugs from bug.list".

## Fixed (on main)

### Allowlist / secrets / edit
- [x] `src/safety/policy.ts` ‚Äî "always approve" broken for cwd-root files (`README.md` ‚Üí `./**/*.ext` never matched). Now derives `**/*.ext`.
- [x] `src/config/schema.ts` ‚Äî secret denylist root-only (`.env*`, `*.pem`, ‚Ä¶). Now `**/`-prefixed so `packages/app/.env` is denied.
- [x] `src/tools/edit.ts` ‚Äî success message reported match count, not replaced count when `occurrences` < matches.

### Agent / compact / forge
- [x] `src/agent/loop.ts` ‚Äî provider fallback never rebuilt the adapter (model name only). Now calls `createProvider` on fallback.
- [x] `src/agent/loop.ts` ‚Äî `SKY-E-2003` hard-killed long audits at 25 tool rounds. Default `sessions.maxIterations` = 60; soft wrap-up summary instead of error.
- [x] `src/session/compact.ts` ‚Äî auto-compact used lifetime `tokenUsage` ‚Üí perpetual explore‚Üíforget loop. Triggers on current history only; protects recent tool results.
- [x] Forge dashboard connect could not list repos ‚Äî added `forge` tool (`status` / `whoami` / `repos` / `repo`).
- [x] OpenCode `Upstream request failed` 400 mapped as hard `SKY-E-5010` ‚Äî now retryable provider flake.

### TUI / Termux
- [x] `src/tui/stream.ts` ‚Äî input "staircase" while typing (`s`‚Üí`sc`‚Üí`scan bug` on new lines). `preferSimpleTui` only checked Android env vars, so forced `SKY_TUI=ink` and proot-Android distros (UserLAnd/Andronix, which strip TERMUX_/ANDROID_ vars) still used Ink and stacked every keystroke. Now the line UI is chosen whenever the terminal cannot rewrite in place (`!supportsLiveStreamRewrite`), and `isTermuxLike` also detects Android via `/system/bin/sh` ¬∑ `/system/build.prop`.
- [x] `src/cli/runtime.ts` ‚Äî `attachMcp` re-connected every MCP server on **every** readline-loop turn (`runTurn` calls it per submission), leaking child processes and re-registering tools. Now idempotent via `runtime.mcpAttached`.

### Shell / cost / dashboard / misc
- [x] `src/safety/shell.ts` ‚Äî pipe-to-shell denylist missed `| /bin/sh` and `| /usr/bin/bash`.
- [x] `src/llm/cost.ts` ‚Äî `MODEL_PRICING` only 4 models; palette models estimated $0. Expanded + prefix lookup.
- [x] `src/session/store.ts` ‚Äî corrupt interior index line tolerated when file lacked trailing `\n`.
- [x] `src/safety/glob.ts` ‚Äî `matchCommandPattern` did not escape `?` (treated as regex quantifier).
- [x] `src/cli/dashboard.ts` ‚Äî `DELETE /api/forge/default` deleted a forge named `default` instead of clearing the default pointer.
- [x] `src/cli/dashboard.ts` ‚Äî forge writes via `loadConfig({ cwd })` persisted project `.skyrc` into `~/.sky/config.json`. Now `skipProject`.
- [x] `src/cli/prompter.ts` ‚Äî empty Enter defaulted to approve. Now denies.
- [x] `src/skills/loader.ts` ‚Äî frontmatter close via `indexOf('---', 3)` broke on `----`. Line-bounded `---` required.
- [x] `src/tools/git.ts` ‚Äî `log` passed non-numeric `args[0]` to `-n`. Sanitized to positive int or `10`.

## Open / watch

_(none from the 2026-07-21 scan ‚Äî all correctness + edge cases above landed on main.)_

## Notes (not bugs)

- `src/safety/glob.ts` ‚Äî `matchGlob` compiled the same regex twice (perf; mitigated).
- `src/llm/context.ts` ‚Äî Pass 2 recomputes token counts each iteration (O(n¬≤), fine at current sizes).
- Free OpenCode flash models still over-explore; prefer targeted prompts (`bugs in src/safety only`) and `/new` after heavy compact.

## How to re-scan

```text
/new
Audit src/safety and src/agent for bugs. List as bullets. Do not re-read the whole repo.
```

Or: `read bug.list` then continue from **Open / watch**.
